%%%
%%% TITLE
%%%
{\large\bfseries Filament Dynamics in the Super-X Divertor Geometry of MAST-Upgrade}\\
~\\
%%%
%%% AUTHOR(S)
%%%
N. R. Walkden${}^{a,b}$, B. D. Dudson${}^{b}$, G. Fishpool${}^{a}$, J. Leddy${}^{b}$, J. Omotani${}^{a}$ and M. Umansky${}^{c}$\\
~\\
%%%
%%% AFFILIATION
%%%
